# Project Setup

This project uses **UV** for dependency management. All Python commands must be run through UV.

```bash
uv lock # Recreate lock
uv lock --upgrade
uv sync # Install dependencies
uv sync --no-dev # For production cases
uv add {package}
uv add --dev {package} # Adds to the development group
uv remove {package}
uv run pytest
uv export --format requirements.txt
```
